### Workflow - Purchase Claim APIs (소유권 등록)
### Consumer: isAuthenticated() only
### Admin: PURCHASE_CLAIM_APPROVE

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@consumerAccessToken = REPLACE_CONSUMER_ACCESS_TOKEN
@adminAccessToken = REPLACE_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN
@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@evidenceGroupId = null
@evidenceId = REPLACE_EVIDENCE_ID
@uploadUrl = REPLACE_UPLOAD_URL
@claimId = REPLACE_CLAIM_ID

## ──────────────────────────────────────
## Consumer APIs
## ──────────────────────────────────────

### 1) Presign evidence upload (소비자)
# @name presignClaimEvidence
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/evidence/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{consumerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "evidenceGroupId": {{evidenceGroupId}},
  "fileName": "receipt-photo.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("evidenceGroupId", response.body.evidenceGroupId);
  client.global.set("evidenceId", response.body.evidenceId);
  client.global.set("uploadUrl", response.body.uploadUrl);
%}

### 2) Upload file to presigned URL
PUT {{uploadUrl}}
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./files/receipt-photo.jpg

### 3) Complete evidence upload (소비자)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/evidence/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{consumerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "evidenceGroupId": "{{evidenceGroupId}}",
  "evidenceId": "{{evidenceId}}",
  "sizeBytes": 102400,
  "fileHash": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}

### 4) Submit purchase claim (소비자)
# @name submitPurchaseClaim
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims
Authorization: Bearer {{consumerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "serialNumber": "SN-001",
  "modelName": "Model X",
  "evidenceGroupId": "{{evidenceGroupId}}",
  "note": "구매 영수증 첨부"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("claimId", response.body.claimId);
%}

### 5) List my claims (소비자)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/me
Authorization: Bearer {{consumerAccessToken}}

## ──────────────────────────────────────
## Admin APIs
## ──────────────────────────────────────

### 6) List pending claims (관리자)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### 7) List claim evidences (관리자)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/{{claimId}}/admin-evidences
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### 8) Approve claim (관리자 → 자동 MINT + 소유권 할당)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/{{claimId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "manufacturedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "productionBatch": "B1",
  "factoryCode": "F1"
}

### 9) Reject claim (관리자)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/purchase-claims/{{claimId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "시리얼 번호 불일치"
}
